snippet.title: Best VGM 1336 - Rayman Origins - Land Of Dead World
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii / Xbox 360 / PS3 / Vita / PC / 3DS
Rayman Origins (2011)
Land Of Dead World (Land of the Livid Dead ~ Nowhere to Run ~ Chasing a Dream)
Christophe Héral & Billy Martin
